expression = re.compile(rfc._EXTENTION_AV_REGEX)
good_examples = ['some random text',
    'any$%^&thing)(* but not ctl chars or semi:']
for good_example in good_examples:
    self.assertTrue(bool(expression.fullmatch(good_example)), msg=
        "Good Extension AV '{m}' not matched by regex".format(m=good_example))
